articleList.title: 111 Vanuatu faces 12-month recovery as Cyclone Harold heads for Fiji
articleList.desc: Disaster officials in the small Pacific nation of Vanuatu work around the clock to assess the damage that a category five cyclone caused to remote islands, as Cyclone Harold heads for Fiji.
